articles.title: Angels GM: Shohei Ohtani declined imaging after Aug. 3 exit - ESPN - ESPN
articles.description: Shohei Ohtani declined imaging after he left an Aug. 3 start against Seattle after four innings because of cramping in his pitching hand and fingers, Los Angeles Angels general manager Perry Minasian said Saturday.
